graph TD
    A[dnlc_lookup: dp, name, cred] --> B{name > 15 chars?}
    B -->|yes| C[Return NULL: too long]
    B -->|no| D[Compute NC_HASH]
    D --> E[Search hash bucket]
    E --> F{Entry found?}
    F -->|no| G[ncstats.misses++]
    F -->|yes| H[ncstats.hits++]
    G --> I[Return NULL: miss]
    H --> J[Move to LRU tail]
    J --> K[Return vp: hit!]
